{"tid":2157362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「洋五毛」覺醒！愛中國變反共鬥士 YouTube闢海外戰線「圍中」","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:28.000Z","uid":343294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"311b76431b40b86c8ef76ef0b54615dfeb82bea5","tid":2157362,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"樂樂法利（Lele Farley），一名熱愛中國文化的德州小子，曾在中國擔任非專業演員，為《人民日報》當繙譯、當《春晚》主持，是準「洋五毛」；英提扎（Inty），一名嘗過中國種族歧視的新疆人，移居美國後閒餘拍片教編程，過得很chill。<br />\n<br />\n然而，中國在總加速師習近平的領導下圖窮匕現，財大氣粗、無視人權的態度，激發起他倆反共決心。擁抱普世價值的二人殊途同歸，成為海外戰線的YouTuber，也與港人連成一氣，全球圍中！<br />\n<br />\n樂樂自稱並不是高尚，不是他不舔共，而是心中仍有底線，不夠舔共，多次錯失當著名「洋五毛」的機會。他說：「（大外宣）不僅僅是我不相信，是從頭到尾bullshxt，我根本不能說是演戲就行，而是他們希望我用外國人身份，告訴大家中國越來越強大，中國被全世界誤解了。」2018年樂樂決定鑽研中英雙語說唱，再到上海戲劇學院進修。在同一年習近平修憲，正式廢除總書記任期，欲永續「習帝」。他回來看到的上海，已是景物依舊，人面全非。他說：「習近平提倡民族主義、排外思想，連我身邊腦子比較聰明的人，也慢慢的被忽悠（欺騙）。我沒想到這些洗腦的措施，果然這樣有效。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n樂樂法利youtube<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyYlGTZL-HnnX_UcGkVFH7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyYlGTZL-HnnX_UcGkVFH7A&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=6ca86789\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyYlGTZL-HnnX_UcGkVFH7A</a><br />\n<br />\n新疆人英提扎（Inty）youtube <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCA3-DEkClR3G1DG1cq8YbeQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCA3-DEkClR3G1DG1cq8YbeQ&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=e11baade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCA3-DEkClR3G1DG1cq8YbeQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: apple daily <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200815/7YDSEK4DFBAIXCMKXK45NXBT3U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR28jRftnQi4XGQrcQP7ZnAFUa1kf0j6ubyMPRZfX4pG2c_JjkjmUat4cxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200815%2F7YDSEK4DFBAIXCMKXK45NXBT3U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR28jRftnQi4XGQrcQP7ZnAFUa1kf0j6ubyMPRZfX4pG2c_JjkjmUat4cxo&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8frgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=82571c9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200815%2F7YDSEK4DFBAIXCMKXK45NXBT3U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR28jRftnQi4XGQrcQP7ZnAFUa1kf0j6ubyMPRZfX4pG2c_JjkjmUat4cxo&h=4e7b4b17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200815/7YDSEK4DFBAIXCMKXK45NXBT3U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR28jRftnQi4XGQrcQP7ZnAFUa1kf0j6ubyMPRZfX4pG2c_JjkjmUat4cxo</a>"},{"pid":"c7599c907b7777ab54bc4b144cb1e3af41ceb945","tid":2157362,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cda5ed72bfb53e19321cc43f90c55f4a9f600b","tid":2157362,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}